          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">‚úì</span>
          <div>
            <h4>Containers</h4>
            <p>rdf:Bag, rdf:Seq, rdf:Alt</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">‚úì</span>
          <div>
            <h4>Collections</h4>
            <p>rdf:List with parseType</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">‚úì</span>
          <div>
            <h4>parseType Variations</h4>
            <p>Resource, Literal, Collection</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">‚úì</span>
          <div>
            <h4>XML Base</h4>
            <p>xml:base attribute support</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">‚úì</span>
          <div>
            <h4>Language Tags</h4>
            <p>xml:lang attribute support</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">‚úì</span>
          <div>
            <h4>Datatyped Literals</h4>
            <p>rdf:datatype attribute</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">‚úì</span>
          <div>
            <h4>Blank Nodes</h4>
            <p>Anonymous and labeled</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">‚úì</span>
          <div>
            <h4>RDF Reification</h4>
            <p>Statement reification</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">‚úì</span>
          <div>
            <h4>Namespace Prefixes</h4>
            <p>Custom and automatic</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">‚úì</span>
          <div>
            <h4>XML Entities (Parsing)</h4>
            <p>DOCTYPE entity declarations</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section standards-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Standards & Specifications</h2>

      <div class="standards-grid">
        <a
          href="https://www.w3.org/TR/rdf-syntax-grammar/"
          class="standard-card"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <h3>RDF/XML Syntax Specification</h3>
          <p>W3C Recommendation for RDF/XML syntax and grammar</p>
        </a>

        <a
          href="https://www.w3.org/TR/rdf11-concepts/"
          class="standard-card"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <h3>RDF 1.1 Concepts</h3>
          <p>Core RDF concepts and abstract syntax</p>
        </a>

        <a
          href="https://www.w3.org/TR/rdf11-primer/"
          class="standard-card"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <h3>RDF 1.1 Primer</h3>
          <p>Introduction to RDF with RDF/XML examples</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Parse RDF/XML?</h2>
      <p class="cta-description">
        Start using W3C-compliant RDF/XML in your Dart projects today.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a
          href="https://pub.dev/packages/locorda_rdf_xml"
          class="cta-primary"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">View on pub.dev</a
        >
        <a
          href="https://pub.dev/documentation/locorda_rdf_xml/latest/"
          class="cta-secondary"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">Read API Docs</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

